        "title": "Fix Antigravity Gemini icon lanes and exhausted bar fill",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Show Antigravity Gemini session on the compact icon's top lane and Gemini weekly on the bottom lane.\n- Never borrow a missing Gemini cadence from Claude + GPT quota-summary rows.\n- Preserve current local/model-quota availability fallback when the quota-summary endpoint is unavailable.\n- Render fractional values that round to 0% or 100% as fully empty or full.\n\n## Review and proof\n\n- `swift test list` passes after splitting an Intel Swift type-checker-heavy `#require` expression.\n- Focused icon, render-signature, and warning-marker suite: 51 tests passed.\n- Exact shard 0 command: all 120 groups passed locally.\n- `make check`: format and lint clean.\n- Full branch autoreview against `origin/main`: clean, confidence 0.82.\n- CI failure diagnosed from the surfaced compiler output: Intel Swift could not type-check the compound bitmap lookup inside `#require`; current head moves the lookup outside the macro without changing behavior.\n\nCurrent head: `77b4b7bb`\n\n## Screenshots\n\n<img width=\"302\" height=\"65\" alt=\"Antigravity compact icon quota lanes\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/79d7ee90-e8ce-412e-bdf6-fef28a27b114\" />\n\n<img width=\"160\" height=\"254\" alt=\"Antigravity usage before\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/6567e897-9473-4b84-a63e-59d2f27f6e0e\" />\n\n<img width=\"166\" height=\"254\" alt=\"Antigravity usage after\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a0ea525c-0c1b-4487-b7e3-f591e6b9b599\" />\n",
